data.description: Very nice updated four bedroom to bath colonial on 3 acres in a private setting but close to the main road(Samsonville) for easy access to 209.Beautifully redone hardwood floors throughout,new appliances, counter tops and flooring in the kitchen. Interior of home was freshly painted with new interior and exterior doors. Nice level yard with wooded areas complete the package..
